  "method": [
    "To make the macarons, follow the instructions, using all the ingredients listed except the chopped peanuts. These you add after you have laid out (or piped) the macarons onto the baking sheet and before the 15-minute rest. Just dot each disk with a few pieces of chopped peanut, leave them to rest, then bake.",
    "To make the filling, mix the peanuts with the dulce de leche, stir in the salt, then taste. You want to get a sweetness that is balanced by a fair amount of saltiness, a bit like peanut butter."
  ],
